high_descs: Go right and then left to cross the room and face the dresser with the computer on it.
Pick the gold vase up from the dresser.
Go right and the turn right again and stand at the white safe on the floor.
Put the gold vase in the safe and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a vase in a safe.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then the left to find the computer.
Pick up the vase from the back of the dresser.
Carry the vase and turn to the right, then right again to find the tall white bookshelf.
Open the safe on the floor and place the vase inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a vase from the dresser to the safe.

high_descs: Walk to the dresser ahead of you.
Grab a vase from the dresser.
Walk to the shelf behind you on your right.
Place the vase in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Store a vase in a safe.
